Jingying Xu and John Ryan presented at the [2026 Linguistics Society of America (LSA) Annual Meeting](https://www.xcdsystem.com/lsa/program/a66baA9/index.cfm?pgid=462), held in New Orleans from January 8–10, 2026.

Jingying gave two talks: **(1)** *Learning Telicity in Context: Developmental Evidence from Mandarin Children* and **(2)** *Beyond Truth Conditions: Context Modulates Telicity Interpretation*.

John presented **Reference, Aspect, and Event Completion in Mandarin Sentence Judgments**.
